            </rs>, <rs id="t17490405-21-cd105" type="crimeDate">March 4</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17490405-21-off104 t17490405-21-cd105"></join>.</p>
               <p>The prosecuter varied in his account from what he had said before the Justice.</p>
